---
// Newsletter signup — Buttondown embed
// To activate: sign up at https://buttondown.com (free up to 100 subs)
// then replace BUTTONDOWN_USERNAME below with your handle.
const BUTTONDOWN_USERNAME = "YOUR_USERNAME_HERE";
const isPlaceholder = BUTTONDOWN_USERNAME === "YOUR_USERNAME_HERE";
---

<div class="newsletter-card card-base p-8 my-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">📬 새 글이 올라오면 알려드릴게요</h2>
    <p class="text-[var(--text-color-muted)] mb-6">
        AI · 콘텐츠 · 개발에 대한 글을 매주 1통, 메일로 보내드립니다. 광고 없음. 언제든 구독 취소 가능.
    </p>

    {isPlaceholder ? (
        <div class="placeholder-warning p-4 rounded-md bg-yellow-100 dark:bg-yellow-900/30 text-sm">
            ⚠️ <strong>뉴스레터 비활성화 상태</strong> — Buttondown 가입 후 <code>src/components/Newsletter.astro</code>의 <code>BUTTONDOWN_USERNAME</code>을 본인 핸들로 변경하세요.
        </div>
    ) : (
        <form
            action={`https://buttondown.com/api/emails/embed-subscribe/${BUTTONDOWN_USERNAME}`}
            method="post"
            target="popupwindow"
            onsubmit={`window.open('https://buttondown.com/${BUTTONDOWN_USERNAME}', 'popupwindow')`}
            class="embeddable-buttondown-form flex gap-2 flex-col sm:flex-row"
        >
            <input
                type="email"
                name="email"
                id="bd-email"
                placeholder="your@email.com"
                required
                class="flex-1 px-4 py-2 rounded-md bg-[var(--card-bg)] border border-[var(--line-divider)] focus:outline-none focus:border-[var(--primary)]"
            />
            <input
                type="submit"
                value="구독하기"
                class="px-6 py-2 rounded-md bg-[var(--primary)] text-white font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition cursor-pointer"
            />
        </form>
    )}
</div>

<style>
    .newsletter-card {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--card-bg) 0%, color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 5%, var(--card-bg)) 100%);
    }
</style>
